Following packages are installed using npm in server.
nodemon - server auto restart
express - library
body-parser - process request body
bcrypt - password encryption
cors - cross origin request
dotenv - environment variables
gridfs-stream - file upload
multer & multer-gridfs-storage - upload files locally
helmet - request safety
morgan - logging
jsonwebtoken - authentication
mongoose - mongoDB access

add "type": "module" in package.json to use ES6 import/export instead of require